            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "招商局港口中期盈利跌逾19%　股息維持25港仙",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">招商局港口(00144)公布，上半年盈利35.8億元，按年跌逾19%，中期息維持每股0.25元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：招商局港口官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250331_FI_source-web_00144-SZ-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：招商局港口官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250331_FI_source-web_00144-SZ-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：招商局港口官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集團上半年經常利潤36.4億元，來自港口業務的經常利潤42.2億元，兩者跌12%或以上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上半年收入升逾11%至64.6億元，完成集裝箱吞吐量升逾4%至7485萬個標準箱，散雜貨吞吐量則跌逾4%至2.6億噸。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15215151-%e6%8b%9b%e5%95%86%e5%b1%80%e6%b8%af%e5%8f%a3%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be19%e3%80%80%e8%82%a1%e6%81%af%e7%b6%ad%e6%8c%8125%e6%b8%af%e4%bb%99-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20230830_FI_source-we00144_FB.jpg.webp",
